  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    COVID-19: guidance for food businesses
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Advice for food businesses in response to the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak in the UK.</p>

  </div>
</div>

